{"tid":1230802,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"飲水係唔會補充流失左嘅電解質","createTime":"2019-06-16T10:03:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T10:39:50.000Z","uid":194326,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adf95d1f447696ae9ebed81df971a34c80676d85","tid":1230802,"uid":194326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:03:54.000Z","msg":"如果冇現成，記得帶effervescent 整oral rehydration solution <br />\n<br />\n The &quot;Simple Solution&quot; - Home made Oral Rehydration Salts (ORS) Recipe<br />\nPreparing 1 (one) Litre solution using Salt, Sugar and Water at Home Mix an oral rehydration solution using the following recipe. Ingredients:<br />\n<br />\nSix (6) level teaspoons of Sugar<br />\nHalf (1/2) level teaspoon of Salt<br />\nOne Litre of clean drinking or boiled water and then cooled - 5 cupfuls (each cup about 200 ml.)<br />\nPreparation Method:<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://rehydrate.org/images/diy3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Frehydrate.org%2Fimages%2Fdiy3.gif&h=fdd45d7b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nStir the mixture till the salt and sugar dissolve.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://rehydrate.org/solutions/homemade.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frehydrate.org%2Fsolutions%2Fhomemade.htm&d=p84ZIGfbRlzA5dgw%2Bb26WP3ZlJXgeXtiTXALECG4O5Q%3D&h=d4b7affd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://rehydrate.org/solutions/homemade.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n而家我唔係香港打工，只係知寶礦力可以補充返電解質。"},{"pid":"54efabfca2ac178441edeff11b2291ca78e8665c","tid":1230802,"uid":186152,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:14:00.000Z","msg":"Ok<br />\n遊行人士請呼籲警犬保持克制冷靜<br />\n遊行人士請呼籲警犬保持克制冷靜<br />\n遊行人士請呼籲警犬保持克制冷靜"},{"pid":"bf0c6f16a4de88cf5b9538ba92e532c45da4bf65","tid":1230802,"uid":243923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T10:18:26.000Z","msg":"記住帶支寶礦力先行"},{"pid":"0ce1e93aafd9fd6d02f181a6e907f081836a0e8d","tid":1230802,"uid":73004,"like":0,"